OL,3,CDurham Women Football Club secure long-
OL,4,Cterm future with new investor
OL,6,FDurham Women FC have announced they
OL,7,Fhave signed a takeover deal which will
OL,8,Fsecure the club's long-term future.
OL,10,FGeoff Thompson, a local businessman,
OL,11,Fwho is the Chairman and co-owner of
OL,12,FSouth Shields FC, has agreed to
OL,13,Facquire a majority shareholding in the
OL,14,Fclub, along with backing from his co-
OL,15,Finvestor at SSFC.
OL,17,FIt comes just over a fortnight after
OL,18,FDurham Women warned they could cease
OL,19,Foperations without fresh investment.
