OL,3,CDurham Women Football Club secure long-
OL,4,Cterm future with new investor
OL,6,FUnder the new deal, club founders Lee
OL,7,FSanders and Dawn Hepple will remain as
OL,8,Fshareholders, while the existing
OL,9,Fexecutive management team will
OL,10,Fcontinue to lead the club's day-to-day
OL,11,Foperations.
OL,13,FSpeaking after agreeing the deal, Dawn
OL,14,FHepple, co-founder of Durham Women FC,
OL,15,Fsaid: "We're delighted to have Geoff
OL,16,Fand his team stepping up and securing
OL,17,Fan exciting future for the club.
OL,26,@wD@GOU
