OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1782397117
OL,3,CDurham Women Football Club secure long-
OL,4,Cterm future with new investor
OL,6,F"The support we've received from our
OL,7,Fstaff, players and supporters
OL,8,Fthroughout this process has been
OL,9,Fincredible, and we're truly grateful
OL,10,Ffor it.
OL,12,F"We would also like to thank Patrick
OL,13,Fand Frances Connolly for their
OL,14,Finvaluable support over the past three
OL,15,Fyears, which has helped the club reach
OL,16,Fthis stage.
